HEADWORD: Ejecta
<hw>E*jec"ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[L., neut.
pl. of <ets>ejectus</ets> cast out. See <er>Eject</er>.]</ety>
<def>Matter ejected; material thrown out; <as>as, the <ex>ejecta</ex> of
a volcano; the <ex>ejecta</ex>, or excreta, of the body</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
